LightExt Base
-------------
- htaccess blocked basic json settings file
	- only store basic settings like: default style, enabled plugins, etc...
- Basic Authentication System
	- Login, Register, Forgot Password
- Easy Modular Plugin System
	- The Option to combine frontend and backend functionality at the same time
	allowing you to enable/disable it at the same time.  Grouping front/backend
	sections together.
- Easy to style
	- Option to choose which style you want as the base.